headline: Omnipod Maker Insulet Is In A Buy Zone As Its Market Expands To Millions
summary: Insulet stock hit a new high of 337.84 on Thursday.  The IBD Sector Leader makes the Omnipod insulin pump for people with diabetes.  Insulet is expanding the use of its products to a potential population of millions.
